<chapter xml:id="implementation">
<title>Implementation</title>
<formalpara>
<title>1. create root project folder</title>
<para>
<programlisting language="bash" linenumbering="unnumbered">mkdir spring-boot-parent-example
touch pom.xml</programlisting>
</para>
</formalpara>
<formalpara>
<title>root</title>
<para>
<programlisting language="xml" linenumbering="unnumbered">  &lt;groupId&gt;com.github.daggerok&lt;/groupId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-parent-example&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;version&gt;0.0.1-SNAPSHOT&lt;/version&gt;
  &lt;packaging&gt;pom&lt;/packaging&gt;

  &lt;modules&gt;
    &lt;module&gt;parent&lt;/module&gt;
    &lt;module&gt;library&lt;/module&gt;
    &lt;module&gt;application&lt;/module&gt;
  &lt;/modules&gt;

  &lt;build&gt;
    &lt;defaultGoal&gt;clean package&lt;/defaultGoal&gt;
  &lt;/build&gt;</programlisting>
</para>
</formalpara>
<formalpara>
<title>2. create spring-boot parent project holder by generating it from start.spring.io project: maven type: pom</title>
<para>
<programlisting language="bash" linenumbering="unnumbered">cd spring-boot-parent-example/
mkdir parent
touch parent/pom.xml</programlisting>
</para>
</formalpara>
<formalpara>
<title>parent</title>
<para>
<programlisting language="xml" linenumbering="unnumbered">  &lt;groupId&gt;com.github.daggerok&lt;/groupId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;parent&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;version&gt;0.0.1-SNAPSHOT&lt;/version&gt;
  &lt;packaging&gt;pom&lt;/packaging&gt;

  &lt;parent&gt;
    &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
    &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-parent&lt;/artifactId&gt;
    &lt;version&gt;2.0.3.RELEASE&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;relativePath/&gt; &lt;!-- lookup parent from repository --&gt;
  &lt;/parent&gt;

  &lt;dependencies&gt;
    &lt;dependency&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter&lt;/artifactId&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;

    &lt;dependency&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-test&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;scope&gt;test&lt;/scope&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;
  &lt;/dependencies&gt;

  &lt;build&gt;
    &lt;plugins&gt;
      &lt;plugin&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-maven-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;/plugin&gt;
    &lt;/plugins&gt;

    &lt;defaultGoal&gt;clean package&lt;/defaultGoal&gt;
  &lt;/build&gt;</programlisting>
</para>
</formalpara>
<formalpara>
<title>3. / 4. create maven submodules with parent not spring-boot-parent, but previously create one: <literal>parent</literal></title>
<para>
<programlisting language="bash" linenumbering="unnumbered">mkdir library application
touch library/pom.xml application/pom.xml</programlisting>
</para>
</formalpara>
<formalpara>
<title>library</title>
<para>
